  adapter for PagerDuty Events API v2 (with dedup_key + severity
  mapping), and fan-out guidance (`GODSVIEW_ALERT_WEBHOOK_URLS`
  comma-separated list). Includes security notes on rotating
  leaked webhook URLs and routing keys.

- `scripts/src/verify-alert-webhook.ts` + `verify-alert-webhook`
  pnpm script — posts a synthetic alert matching the exact shape
  the api-server emits (type, severity, message, details,
  timestamp), to any receiver URL. Exits 0 on 2xx, 1 otherwise.
  Doubles as a contract test for custom receivers. Runs without a
